ebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999969713826, \"rank\": 3.0287280952413205e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Engagement\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were 412 billion engagements, an incredible 290 per cent increase on the previous edition of the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"412 billion engagements\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible 290 per cent increase\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous edition\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach also said that Paris 2024 had \\\"demonstrated the unprecedented global appeal of the Olympic Games\\\".\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999969713826, \"rank\": 3.0287280952413205e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.734368137177261e-26, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unprecedented global appeal\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Audiences are following and interacting with the Olympic Games like never before,\\\" the 70-year-old German said.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9323995263691881, \"rank\": 0.06279098309382246, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Audiences\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The independent surveys also demonstrate that people believe that the Olympic Movement's mission to unite the world in peaceful competition is more important than ever in a divided world.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999450719785, \"rank\": 5.49281287489777e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The independent surveys\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"peaceful competition\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"a divided world\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These were Olympic Games of a new era.\\\"\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"a new era\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1772}]}, {\